WEBVTT

00:02.360 --> 00:04.317
[♪♪♪]

00:04.920 --> 00:07.674
ANNOUNCER:
<i>This is the story of two sisters:</i>

00:08.360 --> 00:11.592
<i>Jessica Tate and Mary Campbell.</i>

00:11.840 --> 00:16.357
<i>Jessica lives in a neighbourhood</i>
<i>known as rich.</i>

00:16.560 --> 00:18.119
<i>Jessica likes life.</i>

00:18.320 --> 00:21.199
<i>The only thing about life</i>
<i>she would change, if she could,</i>

00:21.400 --> 00:23.756
<i>is that she would set it all</i>
<i>to music.</i>

00:25.320 --> 00:28.950
<i>The Tates have more secrets</i>
<i>than they do money.</i>

00:31.560 --> 00:34.758
<i>We're approaching</i>
<i>Mary Campbell's house.</i>

00:36.560 --> 00:38.153
<i>Mary, too, likes life.</i>

00:38.360 --> 00:42.195
<i>Unfortunately, life doesn't seem</i>
<i>to be too crazy about her.</i>

00:42.400 --> 00:45.677
<i>As you can see, the Campbells</i>
<i>don't have nearly as much money</i>

00:45.880 --> 00:46.916
<i>as the Tates.</i>

00:47.840 --> 00:51.390
<i>They do, however,</i>
<i>have as many secrets.</i>

00:55.760 --> 00:56.760
[♪♪♪]

00:56.920 --> 00:59.435
ANNOUNCER:
<i>In last week's episode of</i> Soap,
<i>Jessica apologised to Corinne</i>

00:59.640 --> 01:01.393
<i>for having an affair with Peter.</i>

01:01.640 --> 01:03.597
<i>But Corinne refused</i>
<i>to forgive her mother</i>

01:03.800 --> 01:06.360
<i>and moved out of the house</i>
<i>and in with Peter,</i>

01:06.560 --> 01:09.473
<i>leaving Jessica sad</i>
<i>and Chester mad.</i>

01:09.800 --> 01:14.192
<i>Burt received a telegram announcing</i>
<i>the arrival of his other son, Chuck,</i>

01:14.400 --> 01:18.280
<i>and Chuck's little wooden doll, Bob,</i>
<i>who Chuck believes is real.</i>

01:18.480 --> 01:21.518
<i>The Godfather gave Danny</i>
<i>a key to a cabin in the woods</i>

01:21.720 --> 01:23.951
<i>where a gun is hidden</i>
<i>in the fireplace</i>

01:24.160 --> 01:27.676
<i>and told him he must take Burt there</i>
<i>within two days and kill him</i>

01:27.880 --> 01:29.234
<i>or the mob will kill Danny.</i>

01:29.440 --> 01:30.440
<i>Confused?</i>

01:30.600 --> 01:34.389
<i>You won't be</i>
<i>after this week's episode of</i> Soap.

